        "id": 24,
        "title": "Fernandes equals record with Budweiser Goal of the Month award",
        "description": "No player has won the prize more than the Man Utd star whose volley v Burnley was voted September's best",
        "content": "<p>Bruno Fernandes has equalled the record for the most Budweiser Goal of the Month awards after claiming the September 2023 prize for his sublime volleyed winner&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/match/93374\">against Burnley</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"\" title=\"Embedded Tweet\" contenteditable=\"false\">\n<div><iframe id=\"twitter-widget-0\" title=\"Twitter Tweet\" src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/embed/Tweet.html?dnt=false&amp;embedId=twitter-widget-0&amp;%3D%3D&amp;frame=false&amp;hideCard=false&amp;hideThread=false&amp;id=1712800634288672866&amp;lang=en&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.premierleague.com%2Fnews%2F3735165&amp;sessionId=0a216157542c686841e79ed8880ad38efe5480d0&amp;theme=light&amp;widgetsVersion=01917f4d1d4cb%3A1696883169554&amp;width=550px\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" data-tweet-id=\"1712800634288672866\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n<p>It's the third time the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/clubs/12/Manchester-United/overview\">Manchester United</a>&nbsp;midfielder has claimed the award, putting him level with new&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/clubs/163/Luton-Town/overview\">Luton Town</a>&nbsp;signing&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/3724/Andros-Townsend/stats\">Andros Townsend</a>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/23396/Bruno-Fernandes/stats\">Fernandes</a>&nbsp;made a clever run in behind the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/clubs/43/Burnley/overview\">Burnley</a>&nbsp;defence and produced a sensational first-time strike from&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/3156/Jonny-Evans/stats\">Jonny Evans</a>'s long pass into the bottom corner.</p>\n<p>The 29-year-old first won the award in June 2020 for his&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/video/single/1717636\">strike at Brighton &amp; Hove Albion</a>, before taking the prize for a second time in February 2021 after scoring with a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/video/single/2065263\">stunning chip against Everton</a>.</p>\n<h6>Watch all of Fernandes's Budweiser Goal winners</h6>\n<div>\n<div data-script=\"pl_video\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div data-widget=\"video-player_v2\">\n<div id=\"plVideoPlayer3737158\" tabindex=\"-1\" role=\"region\" translate=\"no\" aria-describedby=\"vjs-dock-description-6\" aria-labelledby=\"plVideoPlayer3737158 vjs-dock-title-5\" aria-label=\"Video Player\" data-video-id=\"6338991070112\" data-account=\"2508689025001\" data-webvtt-id=\"\" data-player=\"BvTUJZhBm\" data-embed=\"default\" data-tracker-type=\"VIDEO\" data-tracker-id=\"3737158\" data-tracker-action=\"VIEW\" data-tracker-status=\"false\">\n<div tabindex=\"-1\" aria-disabled=\"false\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div translate=\"yes\" aria-atomic=\"true\" aria-live=\"off\">\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div id=\"vjs-dock-title-5\">Bruno Fernandes' three Budweiser Goal of the Month winners</div>\n<div id=\"vjs-dock-description-6\">No player has won the award more times than the Man Utd star. But which of his three strikes was the best?</div>\n</div>\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\n<button title=\"Play Video\" type=\"button\" aria-disabled=\"false\"></button></div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n<li style=\"list-style-type: none;\">&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n<button></button><button></button></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div><button>ADCCAudio description available</button></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>It marks the seventh time a Man Utd player has won the Budweiser Goal of the Month award, meaning United players have won the prize more times than those from any other club.&nbsp;<br><br>The Portugal international moves above an exclusive club of two-time winners, which includes&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/4288/Kevin-De-Bruyne/stats\">Kevin De Bruyne</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/5178/Mohamed-Salah/stats\">Mohamed Salah</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/4999/Son-Heung-Min/stats\">Son Heung-min</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/players/54312/Miguel-Almir%C3%B3n/stats\">Miguel Almiron</a>.</p>\n<p>Fernandes's goal was chosen as the winner by a panel of experts combined with a public vote, beating&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/news/3715974\">seven other contenders</a>.</p>\n<h6>Also in this series</h6>\n<p>Part 1:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/news/3734764\">Son matches Shearer and Henry with EA SPORTS Player award</a><br>Part 2:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/news/3735014\">Postecoglou makes history as Barclays Manager of the Month</a><br>Part 4:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.premierleague.com/news/3735061\">Sanchez claims Castrol Save of the Month award</a></p>",
        "image": "https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/lmproject-538b3.appspot.com/o/news%2FGBc8Ipef.webp?alt=media&token=0594e5e1-0d8f-4fdd-a134-f6413ac15313",
        "createdAt": "Sun Oct 15 2023",
        "status": 1,
        "isHome": 1
    },
